//    T2  gauss_log_pdf symmetric (z and -z have same value)
//    T3  make_mask alternation
//    T4  mlp_forward output dim
//    T5  coupling_forward returns [y, log_det]
//    T6  coupling inverse recovers input (invertibility)
//    T7  coupling mask=1 positions identity
//    T8  flow_forward returns [z, log_det]
//    T9  flow_inverse recovers from z
